Keith Barry: Brain Hacker - Series 1, Episode 4




Doodle trick

Keith Barry takes four audience members to prove that doodles are more than just a distraction and can say something about our minds! Keith also goes undercover as a psychic on the streets of Dublin, brings Barcelona street scams to the studio and becomes a human lie detector.




Original Air Date: 02-Feb-2014
